      <title>巴西矿商提高稀土产量，挑战中国控制权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/brazilian-miner-boosts-rare-earths-output-in-challenge-to-china-s-grip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国和中国（全球主要的技术关键矿产供应国）之间的贸易摩擦加剧之际，巴西矿业公司 Serra Verde Group 正在加大稀土金属产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/brazilian-miner-boosts-rare-earths-output-in-challenge-to-china-s-grip</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
